
Task 1

step 

1.docker compose -d

create one network 
2. docker create network mynetwork

3. docker network connect mynetwork container_1

4. docker network connect mynetwork container_2

5. docker network connect mynetwork container_3


(optional) 

6. docker inspect mynetwork

go inside one conatiner and check

7. docker exec -it container_1 /bin/bash

8. ping container_2
   (if ping command is not found then install using 
    this coomand 
     apt-get update
      apt-get install inetutils -ping)
9. ping container_3

 repete step 7,8,9 for other container


